        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for interest in FEA’s work and for money for <hi rend="italic">Index</hi>. Sends 1870 volume of <hi rend="italic">Index</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Praises CD’s services to free-thought.</p>
            <p>Asks for CD’s view of the influence of his theory on religion, to use in lecture.</p>
        </abstract>
